snippet: The president, who promised to use the power and prestige of his office to fill coffers for 2014, opened a two-day swing through Northern California.
abstract: President Obama, who promised to use the power and prestige of his office to fill Congressional Democrats' coffers for 2014, opens two-day swing through Northern California.
lead_paragraph: The president, who promised to use the power and prestige of his office to fill coffers for 2014, opened a two-day swing through Northern California.
